reviewText:
very well presented with a lot of good names from the alternative media.
this documentary explains how our country really works as opposed to how the establishment and corporate fake news media want us to believe.
a very reasonable price too for the quality of the material.

Information regarding the truth about who is
Really in power and decisions made for greed and  mind control was  an enlightenment but frightening.
The voiceover actors are not great.  Making it a bit annoying.  Overall, good information.
From a Noble Lie, State of mind, and now Shadowring Free Mind Films brings the facts you need to know before thinking you are not being manipulated from cradle to grave.
If you don't want to take the red pill don't watch this film. If you love Truth - you'll luv anything from these guys!!

Incredible work; impeccable research - all the bases are covered.  Suggestion; this documentary NEEDS a Study Guide; even a basic outline of each chapter (matching DVD chapters) where people can take notes.  Better yet - provide the outline and let listeners fill in the blanks.

This presentation could be the one that makes Americans remember what THEIR duty is.
Extremely enlightening about our government's manipulations in the past.
this dvd has it all ...well done
